Introduction

ONVO TV ("we", "our", or "us") provides movies and series descriptions and enables users to enjoy watching parties with their family and friends. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our App. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your personal data and how we will treat it.

