Additional Guidelines for Watch Parties

Legally Purchased Content Only: All participants in the Watch Party must have legally purchased copies of the content they wish to watch. Using pirated or unauthorized content is strictly prohibited.

No Pirated Content: Sharing or streaming pirated content will result in immediate suspension of your account and may lead to legal action. We are committed to protecting the rights of content creators and adhering to copyright laws.

Family Viewing Compatibility: Ensure that the content you watch is compatible with family viewing features. This includes content that is appropriate for all ages and adheres to family-friendly entertainment standards.

Responsible Use: The Watch Party feature is designed for synchronized, communal viewing of legal content only. Do not use this feature to view or share any inappropriate or illegal material. Misuse of the feature will result in penalties and possible legal consequences.

